select devgr.Name as GroupName, res.* from ( select mtggr.Name, TO_NUMBER(AMRID) as ENDDEVICEID from MTG_ENUM_ED_IN_GROUP mtgen LEFT JOIN MTG_ED_GROUP mtggr ON mtgen.GROUP_ID = mtggr.ID LEFT JOIN MTR_ENDDEVICE mtred on mtred.ID = mtgen.ENDDEVICE_ID WHERE mtggr.GROUPTYPE = 'EEG' and amrsystemID = 1 UNION ALL select mtggr.Name Name, TO_NUMBER(AMRID) as ENDDEVICEID from YFN_ED_IN_DG yfnen LEFT JOIN MTG_ED_GROUP mtggr ON yfnen.DEVICEGROUPID = mtggr.ID LEFT JOIN MTR_ENDDEVICE mtred on mtred.ID = yfnen.ENDDEVICEID WHERE mtggr.GROUPTYPE = 'QEG' and amrsystemID = 1 UNION ALL select Name, ENDDEVICEID from YFN_ED_IN_AHG yfnahg LEFT JOIN YFN_ADHOC_DG yfndg ON yfnahg.DEVICEGROUPID = yfndg.ID
) devgr INNER JOIN (
select schType, sch.id, ddd.ID as DeviceID, ddd.MRID as "MRID", ddd.SERIALNUMBER as SerialNumber, sch.Name as COMTASKNAME, sch.ConnectionMethod, sch.UseDefaultConnectionTask, sch.URGENCY, sps.name, sch.Status, sch.ScheduleName, sch.FREQUENCYVALUE, sch.FREQUENCYUNIT, sch.OFFSETVALUE, sch.OFFSETUNIT from ddc_device ddd left join ( select case when ((comport is not null) OR (exists (select * from DDC_CONNECTIONTASK ct where ct.comserver is not null and ct.id = cte.connectiontask and cte.nextExecutionTimestamp is not null and cte.nextexecutiontimestamp <=utcDT.utcDT))) then 'Busy' when (((comport is null) and not exists (select * from DDC_CONNECTIONTASK ct where ct.comserver is not null and ct.id = cte.connectiontask) and cte.nextexecutiontimestamp <=utcDT.utcDT)) then 'Pending' when ((lastSuccessfulCompletion is null) and (comport is null) and (cte.currentretrycount = 0) and (cte.nextExecutionTimestamp is not null) and (cte.nextExecutionTimestamp > utcDT.utcDT)) then 'Never completed' when ((cte.nextexecutiontimestamp >utcDT.utcDT) and (comport is null) and (cte.currentretrycount > 0)) then 'Retrying' when ((cte.nextExecutionTimestamp is not null) and (cte.nextExecutionTimestamp >utcDT.utcDT) and (cte.lastSuccessfulCompletion is not null) and (cte.lastExecutionFailed = 1) and (cte.currentretrycount = 0)) then 'Failed' when ((cte.comport is null) and (cte.lastSuccessfulCompletion is not null) and (cte.nextexecutiontimestamp >utcDT.utcDT) and (cte.lastExecutionFailed = 0)) then 'Waiting' when (cte.nextExecutionTimestamp is null) then 'Inactive' else '' end status, ct.id, cte.device, ct.Name, pct.Name as ConnectionMethod, cte.UseDefaultConnectionTask, cte.priority as URGENCY, cs.Name as ScheduleName, ns.FREQUENCYVALUE, ns.FREQUENCYUNIT, ns.OFFSETVALUE, ns.OFFSETUNIT, 'shared' as schType from ddc_comtaskexec cte left join sch_comschedule cs on cte.comschedule = cs.id left join sch_nextexecutionspec ns on ns.id = cs.nextexecutionSpec left join sch_comtaskincomschedule ctics on ctics.comschedule = cs.id left join cts_comtask ct on ctics.comtask = ct.id left join ddc_connectiontask conntsk on conntsk.ID = cte.connectiontask left join DTC_PARTIALCONNECTIONTASK pct on pct.ID = conntsk.Partialconnectiontask, ( select extract (day from t) * 24*60*60 + extract (hour from t) * 60*60 + extract (minute from t) * 60 + extract (second from t) utcDT from (select sys_extract_utc(systimestamp)-to_date('01011970','DDMMYYYY') t from dual) ) utcDT where cte.discriminator = 0 and cte.obsolete_date is null
union all
select case when ((comport is not null) OR (exists (select * from DDC_CONNECTIONTASK ct where ct.comserver is not null and ct.id = cte.connectiontask and cte.nextExecutionTimestamp is not null and cte.nextexecutiontimestamp <=utcDT.utcDT))) then 'Busy' when (((comport is null) and not exists (select * from DDC_CONNECTIONTASK ct where ct.comserver is not null and ct.id = cte.connectiontask) and cte.nextexecutiontimestamp <=utcDT.utcDT)) then 'Pending' when ((lastSuccessfulCompletion is null) and (comport is null) and (cte.currentretrycount = 0) and (cte.nextExecutionTimestamp is not null) and (cte.nextExecutionTimestamp > utcDT.utcDT)) then 'Never completed' when ((cte.nextexecutiontimestamp >utcDT.utcDT) and (comport is null) and (cte.currentretrycount > 0)) then 'Retrying' when ((cte.nextExecutionTimestamp is not null) and (cte.nextExecutionTimestamp >utcDT.utcDT) and (cte.lastSuccessfulCompletion is not null) and (cte.lastExecutionFailed = 1) and (cte.currentretrycount = 0)) then 'Failed' when ((cte.comport is null) and (cte.lastSuccessfulCompletion is not null) and (cte.nextexecutiontimestamp >utcDT.utcDT) and (cte.lastExecutionFailed = 0)) then 'Waiting' when (cte.nextExecutionTimestamp is null) then 'Inactive' else '' end status, ct.id, cte.device, ct.Name, pct.Name as ConnectionMethod, cte.UseDefaultConnectionTask, cte.priority as URGENCY, '' as ScheduleName, ns.FREQUENCYVALUE, ns.FREQUENCYUNIT, ns.OFFSETVALUE, ns.OFFSETUNIT, 'individually' as schType from ddc_comtaskexec cte left join cts_comtask ct on cte.comtask = ct.id left join sch_nextexecutionspec ns on ns.id = cte.nextexecutionSpecs left join ddc_connectiontask conntsk on conntsk.ID = cte.connectiontask left join DTC_PARTIALCONNECTIONTASK pct on pct.ID = conntsk.Partialconnectiontask, ( select extract (day from t) * 24*60*60 + extract (hour from t) * 60*60 + extract (minute from t) * 60 + extract (second from t) utcDT from (select sys_extract_utc(systimestamp)-to_date('01011970','DDMMYYYY') t from dual) ) utcDT where cte.discriminator = 1 and cte.obsolete_date is null
union all
select 'Inactive' as Status, ct.id, ddc_device.ID, ct.Name, pct.Name as ConnectionMethod, UseDefaultConnectionTask, cte.priority as URGENCY, '' as ScheduleName, -1 as FREQUENCYVALUE, -1 as FREQUENCYUNIT, -1 as OFFSETVALUE, -1 as OFFSETUNIT, 'non-recurring' as schType from ddc_device left join dtc_deviceconfig dc on ddc_device.DEVICECONFIGID = dc.ID left join dtc_comtaskenablement cte on cte.devicecomconfig = dc.id left join dtc_securitypropertyset sps on sps.ID = cte.securityPropertyset left join cts_comtask ct on cte.comtask = ct.id left join ddc_connectiontask ctk on ctk.device = ddc_device.id and ctk.isdefault = 1 left join DTC_PARTIALCONNECTIONTASK pct on (Usedefaultconnectiontask =0 and pct.id = cte.PARTIALCONNECTIONTASK) or (Usedefaultconnectiontask !=0 and pct.id = ctk.PARTIALCONNECTIONTASK) where
ct.id not in (select comtask from ddc_comtaskexec where discriminator = 1 and obsolete_date is null and device = ddc_device.id) and ct.id not in (select ct.id from ddc_comtaskexec cte left join sch_comschedule cs on cte.comschedule = cs.id left join sch_comtaskincomschedule ctics on ctics.comschedule = cs.id left join cts_comtask ct on ctics.comtask = ct.id where cte.discriminator = 0 and cte.obsolete_date is null and device = ddc_device.id)
) sch on sch.device = ddd.id
left join dtc_deviceconfig dc on ddd.DEVICECONFIGID = dc.ID left join dtc_comtaskenablement cte on cte.devicecomconfig = dc.id and cte.comtask = sch.id left join dtc_securitypropertyset sps on sps.ID = cte.securityPropertyset ) res on devgr.ENDDEVICEID = res.DeviceID

select devgr.Name as GroupName, res.* from ( select mtggr.Name, TO_NUMBER(AMRID) as ENDDEVICEID from MTG_ENUM_ED_IN_GROUP mtgen LEFT JOIN MTG_ED_GROUP mtggr ON mtgen.GROUP_ID = mtggr.ID LEFT JOIN MTR_ENDDEVICE mtred on mtred.ID = mtgen.ENDDEVICE_ID WHERE mtggr.GROUPTYPE = 'EEG' and amrsystemID = 1 UNION ALL select mtggr.Name Name, TO_NUMBER(AMRID) as ENDDEVICEID from YFN_ED_IN_DG yfnen LEFT JOIN MTG_ED_GROUP mtggr ON yfnen.DEVICEGROUPID = mtggr.ID LEFT JOIN MTR_ENDDEVICE mtred on mtred.ID = yfnen.ENDDEVICEID WHERE mtggr.GROUPTYPE = 'QEG' and amrsystemID = 1 UNION ALL select Name, ENDDEVICEID from YFN_ED_IN_AHG yfnahg LEFT JOIN YFN_ADHOC_DG yfndg ON yfnahg.DEVICEGROUPID = yfndg.ID
) devgr INNER JOIN (select dv.ID as DeviceID, dv.MRID as MRID, dv.SERIALNUMBER SerialNumber, dt.Name as DeviceType, dc.Name as DeviceConfig, dv.CERTIF_YEAR as CertificateYear from DDC_DEVICE dv left join DTC_DEVICETYPE dt on dv.DEVICETYPE = dt.ID left join DTC_DEVICECONFIG dc ON dv.DEVICECONFIGID = dc.ID ) res on devgr.ENDDEVICEID = res.DeviceID

select devgr.Name as GroupName, res.* from ( select Name, ENDDEVICE_ID as ENDDEVICEID from MTG_ENUM_ED_IN_GROUP mtgen LEFT JOIN MTG_ED_GROUP mtggr ON mtgen.GROUP_ID = mtggr.ID WHERE mtggr.GROUPTYPE = 'EEG' UNION ALL select Name, ENDDEVICEID from YFN_ED_IN_DG yfnen LEFT JOIN MTG_ED_GROUP mtggr ON yfnen.DEVICEGROUPID = mtggr.ID WHERE mtggr.GROUPTYPE = 'QEG' UNION ALL select Name, ENDDEVICEID from YFN_ED_IN_AHG yfnahg LEFT JOIN YFN_ADHOC_DG yfndg ON yfnahg.DEVICEGROUPID = yfndg.ID ) devgr INNER JOIN ( select gateway.ID as GatewayID, gateway.MRID, ct.device , successindicator , TASKSUCCESSCOUNT , DATE '1970-01-01' + cs.startdate/(24*60*60*1000) ConnectionDate , StopDate , TOTALMILLIS, bytessent, bytesread , MAX((select count(*) from DDC_COMTASKEXECSESSION connDev where connDev.comsession = cs.ID and connDev.startdate between pgr.starttime and pgr.endtime and connDev.device != pgr.gatewayid)) ConnDevices from DTL_PHYSICALGATEWAYREFERENCE pgr left join ddc_device gateway on pgr.gatewayid = gateway.id left join ddc_connectiontask ct on ct.device = gateway.id inner join ddc_comsession cs on cs.connectiontask = ct.id where cs.startdate between pgr.starttime and pgr.endtime group by gateway.ID, gateway.MRID, ct.device, successindicator, TASKSUCCESSCOUNT, StartDate, StopDate , TOTALMILLIS, bytessent, bytesread ) res on devgr.ENDDEVICEID = res.GatewayID

select devgr.Name as GroupName, res.* from ( select Name, ENDDEVICE_ID as ENDDEVICEID from MTG_ENUM_ED_IN_GROUP mtgen LEFT JOIN MTG_ED_GROUP mtggr ON mtgen.GROUP_ID = mtggr.ID WHERE mtggr.GROUPTYPE = 'EEG' UNION ALL select Name, ENDDEVICEID from YFN_ED_IN_DG yfnen LEFT JOIN MTG_ED_GROUP mtggr ON yfnen.DEVICEGROUPID = mtggr.ID WHERE mtggr.GROUPTYPE = 'QEG' UNION ALL select Name, ENDDEVICEID from YFN_ED_IN_AHG yfnahg LEFT JOIN YFN_ADHOC_DG yfndg ON yfnahg.DEVICEGROUPID = yfndg.ID ) devgr INNER JOIN ( select dvs.ID as DeviceID, dvs.MRID deviceMRID, gateway.MRID gatewayMRID, TASKSUCCESSCOUNT, TASKFAILURECOUNT, TASKNOTEXECUTEDCOUNT, TOTALMILLIS, cs.stopdate, DATE '1970-01-01' + cs.startdate/(24*60*60*1000) ConnectionDate from ddc_device dvs inner join DTL_PHYSICALGATEWAYREFERENCE pgr on pgr.originid = dvs.id left join ddc_device gateway on pgr.gatewayid = gateway.id left join ddc_connectiontask ct on ct.device = gateway.id inner join ddc_comsession cs on cs.connectiontask = ct.id where cs.startdate between pgr.starttime and pgr.endtime ) res on devgr.ENDDEVICEID = res.DeviceID

select devgr.Name as GroupName, res.* from ( select Name, ENDDEVICE_ID as ENDDEVICEID from MTG_ENUM_ED_IN_GROUP mtgen LEFT JOIN MTG_ED_GROUP mtggr ON mtgen.GROUP_ID = mtggr.ID WHERE mtggr.GROUPTYPE = 'EEG' UNION ALL select Name, ENDDEVICEID from YFN_ED_IN_DG yfnen LEFT JOIN MTG_ED_GROUP mtggr ON yfnen.DEVICEGROUPID = mtggr.ID WHERE mtggr.GROUPTYPE = 'QEG' UNION ALL select Name, ENDDEVICEID from YFN_ED_IN_AHG yfnahg LEFT JOIN YFN_ADHOC_DG yfndg ON yfnahg.DEVICEGROUPID = yfndg.ID ) devgr INNER JOIN ( SELECT dd.MRID, dd.ID DeviceID, mrt.AliasName Name, DATE '1970-01-01' + LASTREADING/(24*60*60*1000) LastReadingDate, ld.LastReading, ld.LastValue, mrg.Name RegisterGroup FROM DDC_DEVICE dd left join DTC_REGISTERSPEC drs on drs.deviceconfigid = dd.deviceconfigid left join MDS_MEASUREMENTTYPE mmt on mmt.ID = drs.registertypeID left join MTR_READINGTYPE mrt on mrt.MRID = mmt.readingtype left join ( SELECT DISTINCT idsvm2.TIMESERIESID , MAX(idsvm2.RECORDTIME) OVER (PARTITION BY idsvm2.TIMESERIESID) AS LastReading , NVL(to_char(FIRST_VALUE(idsvm2.SLOT1) OVER (PARTITION BY idsvm2.TIMESERIESID ORDER BY idsvm2.RECORDTIME DESC)), FIRST_VALUE(idsvm2.TEXTSLOT0) OVER (PARTITION BY idsvm2.TIMESERIESID ORDER BY idsvm2.RECORDTIME DESC)) AS LastValue , mc.MAINREADINGTYPEMRID , mmac.meterID FROM Ids_Vault_Mtr_2 idsvm2 left join Mtr_Channel mc on idsvm2.Timeseriesid = mc.Timeseriesid left join Mtr_Meteractivation mmac on mc.meteractivationid = mmac.id ) ld on ld.MAINREADINGTYPEMRID = mmt.readingtype and dd.id = meterID LEFT JOIN MDS_REGISTERTYPEINGROUP mrtg on mrtg.registertypeID = mmt.ID LEFT JOIN MDS_REGISTERGROUP mrg on mrg.ID = mrtg.registergroupID ) res on devgr.ENDDEVICEID = res.DeviceID

viewField.SQLClause:
CASE when FREQUENCYVALUE = -1 or FREQUENCYVALUE is null then 'Ad Hoc' when FREQUENCYVALUE =1 then '' else TO_CHAR(FREQUENCYVALUE) end ||' '|| CASE FREQUENCYUNIT when 1 then case when FREQUENCYVALUE=1 then 'Yearly' else 'Years' end when 2 then case when FREQUENCYVALUE=1 then 'Monthly' else 'Months' end when 3 then case when FREQUENCYVALUE=1 then 'Weekly' else 'Weeks' end when 5 then case when FREQUENCYVALUE=1 then 'Daily' else 'Days' end when 11 then case when FREQUENCYVALUE=1 then 'Hourly' else 'Hours' end when 12 then 'Every minute' when 13 then 'Sec' when 14 then 'Milisec' end || case when FREQUENCYVALUE = -1 or FREQUENCYVALUE is null or FREQUENCYUNIT=12 then '' else ', ' end || CASE when OFFSETVALUE = -1 or OFFSETVALUE is null then '' else CASE OFFSETUNIT when 5 then 'Day' when 11 then 'Hour' when 12 then 'Min' when 13 then case when FREQUENCYUNIT = 2 then 'Day '|| case when OFFSETVALUE<86400 then '1' else to_char(TRUNC(OFFSETVALUE/86400)) end || ', ' || to_char(to_date(MOD(OFFSETVALUE, 86400),'sssss'),'hh24:mi:ss') when FREQUENCYUNIT = 5 then to_char(to_date(OFFSETVALUE,'sssss'),'hh24:mi:ss') when FREQUENCYUNIT = 11 then to_char(to_date(OFFSETVALUE,'sssss'),'mi:ss')
end when 14 then 'Milisec' end end
Case when USEDEFAULTCONNECTIONTASK = 1 then case when CONNECTIONMETHOD is null then '' else CONNECTIONMETHOD || ' ' || '(Default)' end else CONNECTIONMETHOD end

CASE when FREQUENCYVALUE = -1 or FREQUENCYVALUE is null then 'Ad Hoc' when FREQUENCYVALUE =1 then '' else TO_CHAR(FREQUENCYVALUE) end ||' '|| CASE FREQUENCYUNIT when 1 then case when FREQUENCYVALUE=1 then 'Yearly' else 'Years' end when 2 then case when FREQUENCYVALUE=1 then 'Monthly' else 'Months' end when 3 then case when FREQUENCYVALUE=1 then 'Weekly' else 'Weeks' end when 5 then case when FREQUENCYVALUE=1 then 'Daily' else 'Days' end when 11 then case when FREQUENCYVALUE=1 then 'Hourly' else 'Hours' end when 12 then 'Min' when 13 then 'Sec' when 14 then 'Milisec' end || case when FREQUENCYVALUE = -1 or FREQUENCYVALUE is null then '' else ', ' end || CASE when OFFSETVALUE = -1 or OFFSETVALUE is null then '' else CASE OFFSETUNIT when 5 then 'Day' when 11 then 'Hour' when 12 then 'Min' when 13 then case when FREQUENCYUNIT = 2 then 'Day '|| to_char(TRUNC(OFFSETVALUE/86400)) || ', ' || to_char(to_date(MOD(OFFSETVALUE, 86400),'sssss'),'hh24:mi:ss') when FREQUENCYUNIT = 5 then to_char(to_date(OFFSETVALUE,'sssss'),'hh24:mi:ss') when FREQUENCYUNIT = 11 then to_char(to_date(OFFSETVALUE,'sssss'),'mi:ss')
end when 14 then 'Milisec' end end
CASE WHEN DEVICE is not null then 1 else null end
CASE WHEN DEVICE is not null then 1 else null end
Case when LASTVALUE is null then '-' when INSTR(NAME, 'Wh') > 0 then to_char(to_number(LASTVALUE), '999,999,999,999,999') || ' Wh' else to_char(LASTREADING) end
